{"tid":1057005,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港區人大王敏剛病逝 終年70歲","createTime":"2019-03-11T14:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T23:15:51.000Z","uid":24781,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ae53c52392e9fc481b3ba6fcc1a95ab03fbbfd","tid":1057005,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"有報道指，香港船王王華生的長子、港區人大代表王敏剛在今日（11日）傍晚6時病逝，終年70歲。王敏剛連續6屆擔任港區人大代表，本月因健康問題，缺席全國人大會議。《星島日報》網上報道指，當時王指自己因肝膽問題，醫生稱他不適合開會，因此請假休養。<br />\n王敏剛在1949年1月出於造船世家，擁有美國加州大學機械工程系學士，1987年獲委任為香港太平紳士，1988年獲香港工業總會頒香港青年工業家獎；上世紀90年代開始涉足政治，1997至1999年獲委任為臨時市政局議員，2003年獲頒銅紫荊星章。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190311/59358194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190311%2F59358194&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6Ke24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=ea1bf899\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190311%2F59358194&h=e10aa2c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190311/59358194</a><br />\n<br />\n落去搵毛主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7ab84570ca83fd0e70232082b870e485d3e6ba","tid":1057005,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦，仆街賣港賊"},{"pid":"216b4b50a27349f35341a4f966c15c84d216d027","tid":1057005,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T22:42:44.000Z","msg":"死多幾件啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1046be841a1aa2e0285e4dc86718bb2a547b77fe","tid":1057005,"uid":83348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T22:56:39.000Z"